[BTCPak](https://www.btcpak.com) is a service to exchange your [[Bitcoins]] for [[MoneyPak]].  The service is requires the user to select the denomination of MoneyPak they would like to receive and provide a [[bitcoin_address]] in case a refund is necessary.


The user is then provided with a [[bitcoin_address]] to send the provided number of [[Bitcoins]].  After six network confirmations, the user is presented with the [[MoneyPak]] code.  If the user deposits using a [[GreenAddress]] from [[MtGox]] or [[Instawallet]], the [[MoneyPak]] code is available immediately.

##History

* Site was launched February 21st, 2012.

##Green Addresses Accepted

* [[MtGox]]
* [[Instawallet]]

